    "source_section_latex": "\\[ H_{\\mathrm{rot}} = -\\hbar\\, \\Omega\\cdot J, \\] \\[ \\rho_{\\mathrm{bif}} = \\mathrm{TensorDecompose}\\!\\bigl(-2\\,\\Omega \\times (\\rho \\otimes p)\\bigr), \\] \\[ \\gamma_{\\mathrm{B}} = \\int_{0}^{2\\pi/\\Omega} \\langle \\psi(t) \\mid i\\,\\rho_{\\mathrm{median}} = 0 \\mid \\psi(t)\\rangle\\,dt. \\] The operator is the ordered triple formed by these three components.\n\n\\[\nH_{\\mathrm{rot}} = -\\hbar\\,\\Omega\\!\\cdot\\!J\n\\]\n\\[\nU(t) = \\exp\\!\\left(-i H_{\\mathrm{rot}} t/\\hbar\\right)\n\\]"
